the pleasures of life.

00:20:47.860 --> 00:20:49.727
Things like good food,

00:20:49.727 --> 00:20:53.775
a drink with friends
after a long week of work,

00:20:53.775 --> 00:20:57.158
falling in love, that's
a great thing in life,

00:20:57.158 --> 00:20:59.137
spending time with family.

00:20:59.137 --> 00:21:02.328
These are all undoubtedly great things

00:21:02.328 --> 00:21:05.132
that we enjoy in our lives.

00:21:05.132 --> 00:21:07.494
I'd also argue that sleep is

00:21:07.494 --> 00:21:10.134
one of those great things in our lives.

00:21:10.134 --> 00:21:12.142
There's nothing better than sleep

00:21:12.142 --> 00:21:13.898
when you're truly tired,

00:21:13.898 --> 00:21:15.974
and the feeling of climbing into bed,

00:21:15.974 --> 00:21:17.455
pulling up the covers,

00:21:17.455 --> 00:21:21.599
putting your head down and
falling asleep is pure bliss.

00:21:21.599 --> 00:21:25.468
And we see this in cases of
extreme sleep deprivation.

00:21:25.468 --> 00:21:26.301
